
DESCRIPTION

    A script to recursively convert regular files ending in a WAV
    extension to FLAC, and MP3, WMA to OGG. And remove files ending
    with INI, DB and JPG extensions.

SOFTWARE REQUIREMENTS

    bash
    mplayer - for WMA support
    lame - for MP3 support
    vorbis-tools - for OGG support
    flac - for FLAC support

CREDITS

    audio-convert, by thetroublemaker,
        http://freecode.com/projects/audio-convert

